high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up a dirty towel from the counter.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Put the dirty towel in the bathtub.
Turn right and go to the counter by the bathtub.
Pick up a dirty towel from the counter.
Turn left and go to the bathtub.
Put the dirty towel in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Move dirty towels to the bathtub.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk over to the bath tub at the end of the room
grab the cloth off of the right side of the bathroom tub
move to the left a bit to face the center of the bath tub
place the cloth inside of the bath tub
move to the right to go back to the right side of the bath tub again
grab the cloth off of the bath tub
move to the left a bit to face the center of the bath tub
place the cloth inside of the bath tub
anns.task_desc: place two cloth's inside of the bath tub

high_descs: Turn right go forward, then turn left and go forward to approach the counter.
Pick up the nearest rag from the counter, to the right of the sink.
Go to the sink to your left.
Put the rag in the sink.
Return to the counter to your right.
Pick up the rag on the counter.
Go to the sink to your left.
Put the rag in the sink, next to the other rag.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags in the sink.

high_descs: Move to the tub and stand at the end closest to the window.
Pick up the wash cloth that's closest to you from the edge of the tub.
Carry the wash cloth to stand at the center point of the tub.
Place the wash cloth in the water of the tub.
Move back to stand at the end of the tub closest to the window.
Pick up the other wash cloth that's near the wall.
Move back to stand lined up with the center of the tub.
Place the wash cloth in the water in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths to the water in the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the wall, turn left, go to the right side of the bath tub.
Take the closest rag from the bath tub platform
Turn left, go to the center of the bath tub, turn right to face the bath tub.
Put the rag in the rag in the middle of the bath tub.
Turn right, go to the wall, turn left to face the right side of the bath tub.
Take the rag from the bath tub platform.
Turn left, go to the center of the bath tub, turn right to face the bath tub.
Put the rag in the rag to the left of the other rag.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags in a bath tub.
